
*** Smart Budget & Expense + Financial Assistant 
*** Expense Ingestion
*** Upload CSVs, bank statements, or receipts (OCR)

Manual entry through UI
Categorization
Auto-categorize expenses (e.g., Food, Bills, Travel)
Editable by user
Dashboard Summary
Monthly spend
Top categories
Comparison to previous months

Natural Language Queries
"How much did I spend on food last week?"
"What are my top 3 expenses this month?"
Savings & Budget Goals
Set monthly budgets per category
Get alerts when nearing limits






